DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that the user cannot change their password if the new password and confirmation password do not match.
NAME: Change Password with Mismatched Confirmation

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that the user cannot log in with invalid credentials and receives an appropriate error message.
NAME: Invalid Login Test

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that the user can log in with valid credentials and is redirected to the account page.
NAME: Valid Login Test

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that a user can change their password successfully when all fields are entered correctly.
NAME: Change Password Successfully

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that a user cannot change their password using an incorrect current password.
NAME: Change Password with Incorrect Current Password
